        "description": "Sommad gets you on an adventure in a self-overlapping VR maze. The game has two modes, Action and Puzzle mode. Walk freely and challenge your skills fighting enemies and solving puzzles! \n\nThe maze and its map use the core mechanic of “non-euclidean architectures (impossible spaces)\", which allows for exploring without teleportation required! \nKey features include: Finding keys, solving puzzles, fighting enemies, avoiding and decharging robots and obstacles, platforms and a map of the level.\n\nKey features include: \n● Finding keys to unlock doors\n● Over 60 clever and unique puzzles\n● Explore 5 beautifully designed worlds\n● Combat enemies\n● Around 5–6 hours playtime\n● Obstacles and moving platforms \n● Maps for all worlds\n● Leaderboards\n\nSommad recommended play space: 2.5m x 2m\nMinimum play space: 2m x 2m",
